title: The Simple Beauty of PowerWash Simulator
description:
Power wash simulator is a game. A game I could probably explain in 2 sentences, but I won’t, because I made this 9 minute video to do it instead.

As far as games go, it’s quite good. As far as games about power washing go, it’s exceptional. As far as games go about power washing that I’m making a video about this week, it’s possibly the greatest game ever made.
